      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "═══════════════════════════════════════════\n📝 UNIVERSAL JSON to PROMPT\n═══════════════════════════════════════════\n\n📌 HOW TO USE:\n1️⃣ Paste your JSON into the field above\n2️⃣ Use the format field to create your prompt template\n3️⃣ Key fields are pre-configured with common alternatives\n4️⃣ Output automatically connects to conditioning nodes\n\n💡 Example JSON structure:\n{\n  \"subject\": {\n    \"hair\": \"long dark curly\",\n    \"skin\": \"fair\"\n  },\n  \"clothing\": {\n    \"top\": \"red cardigan\"\n  }\n}\n\n💬 Format example: \n\"A {subject.hair} hair woman with {subject.skin} skin wearing {clothing.top}\"\n\n📤 Prompt preview appears in the left window\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════════"
      ],
      "color": "#232",
      "bgcolor": "#353"
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
