        }
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "═══════════════════════════════════════════\n💾 SEED VAULT PRO\n═══════════════════════════════════════════\n\n📌 HOW TO USE:\n1️⃣ Select Mode: \n   🤖 auto_save  - Save automatically every run\n   ✍️ manual_save - Save only when approved\n   🔄 update_only - Update notes only (no image)\n\n2️⃣ Fill in the fields:\n   📝 Prompt Summary - Short description\n   💬 Notes - Detailed observations\n   ⭐ Rating - 1-10 score\n   🏷️ Tags - Comma separated keywords\n\n3️⃣ ⚠️ IMPORTANT: Settings are MANUAL!\n   You MUST enter these values yourself:\n   ⚙️ CFG, Steps, Sampler, Clip Skip, LoRAs\n   → They are NOT auto-detected from KSampler!\n   → Enter the SAME values you use in KSampler\n\n4️⃣ Click Approve (only in manual mode)\n\n💡 Everything is automatically saved!\n\n📁 IMPORTANT: Set your vault_path correctly!\n   ⚠️ Use FULL PATH to your seed_vault folder\n   ✅ Example: \"C:/ComfyUI_windows_portable/ComfyUI/output/seed_vault/\"\n   ✅ Example: \"/Users/username/ComfyUI/output/seed_vault/\"\n   \n🖼️ Images are stored in: [your_path]/images/\n📋 Seed list appears in the right window\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════════"
      ],
